// ✅ UPDATED: Handles PredictionResponse instead of PredictedBasket | null
// ✅ FIXED: Proper checking for response.basket.items existence  
// ✅ ADDED: Infinite duration for specific error messages (no time limit)
// ✅ IMPROVED: Clear distinction between business logic errors and system errors
// ✅ PRESERVED: All existing visual variants and functionality
// 
// Now displays exact backend messages like: "⚠️ User needs at least 3 orders for predictions"
// ============================================================================